import Navbar from '../components/Navbar' import {useState} from "react" import {useCookies} from "react-cookie" const OnBoarding = () => { const [cookies, setCookie, removeCookie] = useCookies(['user']) const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ user_Id: cookies.UserId, first_name: "", dob_day: "", dob_month: "", dob_year: "", show_gender: false, gender_identity: "man", gender_interest: "woman", url: "", about: "", matches: [] }) const handleSubmit = async () => { console.log('submitted') } const handleChange = (e) => { console.log('e', e) const value = e.target.type === 'checkbox'? e.target.checked: e.target.value const name = e.target.name setFormData((prevState) => ({ ...prevState, [name] : value })) } console.log(formData) return ( <> {}} showModal={false} />

) } export default OnBoarding
